        Constructor for a new concrete points challenge. This constructor needs to be called to retrieve an existing challenge, not to create a new one.
        Parameters:
        id - unique identifier of the challenge.
        founderID - Id of the founder
        challengeName - challenge name.
        users - users who joined the challenge.
        creationDateTime - challenge creation date
        startDateTime - challenge start date
        finishDateTime - challenge finish date
        durationInDays - challenge duration (given in days)
        founderUri - URI of the founder profile picture
        status - challenge status
        userIDPointsMap - current user ranking
        userIDUsernameMap - map between user ID and user names
